                    "body": "Working today with ZF svn ( 17420) and a table with a binary col, I've been hit by the same bug.\nIs there any work around for this. Parameters setting or something ? \n\nWith native pdo the update works like a charm.\n\nI've try the given patch (v3) but wihout success ?\n\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
